{"talk":{"id":2651,"name":"Paul Knoepfler: The ethical dilemma of designer babies","description":"Creating genetically modified people is no longer a science fiction fantasy; it's a likely future scenario. Biologist Paul Knoepfler estimates that within fifteen years, scientists could use the gene editing technology CRISPR to make certain \"upgrades\" to human embryos -- from altering physical appearances to eliminating the risk of auto-immune diseases. In this thought-provoking talk, Knoepfler readies us for the coming designer baby revolution and its very personal, and unforeseeable, consequences.","slug":"paul_knoepfler_the_ethical_dilemma_of_designer_babies","recorded_at":"2015-10-31 00:00:00","published_at":"2017-01-23 16:18:29","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:46:21","viewed_count":1345918,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":175,"name":"TEDxVienna"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c32f3b131610db35f82f1a5abb97645fc94469a6_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c32f3b131610db35f82f1a5abb97645fc94469a6_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c32f3b131610db35f82f1a5abb97645fc94469a6_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c32f3b131610db35f82f1a5abb97645fc94469a6_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/380f7ff8bdaa85f87e96fe0f4dbff5aa79f00178_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/PaulKnoepfler_2015X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":9046768,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/PaulKnoepfler_2015X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":25075187,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/PaulKnoepfler_2015X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","fi